{"title":"给自己的xxx系统加一个富文本编辑器？还是直接上markdown吧","slug":"2020011001","date":"2020-01-10T14:37:23.000Z","updated":"2020-01-10T14:37:29.266Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/2020011001.json","excerpt":"大家也肯定都碰到过，在做xxx系统的时候，如果要评论或者发一篇文章，总不能用textarea去写吧，一开始，包括我也一样，去github找一个开源的富文本编辑器，这样就有效的避免了textarea内容单一的问题，但它也不是一个完美的解决方案，html格式的串如果直接存储到DB的话，会有很多的标签，这样会无形间加大DB的压力，同时，在内容回显，又容易被页面自带样式所影响，直接进行的富文本编辑对编辑者也有一定的要求，就像微信公众号一样，如果审美不好会显得非常难看….","covers":["https://pic.downk.cc/item/5e1888947f9a96fec1634e6a.jpg","https://pic.downk.cc/item/5e188a527f9a96fec163a538.jpg","https://pic.downk.cc/item/5e188baf7f9a96fec163d9aa.jpg"],"content":"<p>大家也肯定都碰到过，在做xxx系统的时候，如果要评论或者发一篇文章，总不能用textarea去写吧，一开始，包括我也一样，去github找一个开源的富文本编辑器，这样就有效的避免了textarea内容单一的问题，但它也不是一个完美的解决方案，html格式的串如果直接存储到DB的话，会有很多的标签，这样会无形间加大DB的压力，同时，在内容回显，又容易被页面自带样式所影响，直接进行的富文本编辑对编辑者也有一定的要求，就像微信公众号一样，如果审美不好会显得非常难看….</p>\n<a id=\"more\"></a>\n<p>伴随着一系列的问题，大佬们也开始探索更完美的解决方案，而MarkDown语法便是大家目前公认的解决方案之一。它的优点主要就是统一方便的语法，可以让人们专注于创作——难道让我就想加个标题还得前后加个H1标签？<br>之后我便在github上找到了一款国产开源，适配简单的markdown编辑器<a href=\"https://pandao.github.io/editor.md/\">editormd</a>。功能覆盖的很全面，在这里我只说一下编辑模式，阅读模式怎么架到自己的项目里。</p>\n<h3 id=\"下载项目source\"><a href=\"#下载项目source\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"下载项目source\"></a>下载项目source</h3><p><a href=\"https://github.com/pandao/editor.md/archive/master.zip\">点击这里下载</a><br>接着移植的时候只需要以下文件和文件夹即可。<br><img src=\"https://pic.downk.cc/item/5e1888947f9a96fec1634e6a.jpg\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"编辑模式的配置\"><a href=\"#编辑模式的配置\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"编辑模式的配置\"></a>编辑模式的配置</h3><p>1.导包(注意路径)</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight javascript\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&lt;!--CSS--&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;link rel=<span class=\"string\">&quot;stylesheet&quot;</span> href=<span class=\"string\">&quot;editormd/css/editormd.css&quot;</span> /&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;!--JavaScript--&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;script src=<span class=\"string\">&quot;https://cdn.bootcss.com/jquery/1.11.3/jquery.min.js&quot;</span>&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;script src=<span class=\"string\">&quot;editormd/editormd.min.js&quot;</span>&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>2.html</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight javascript\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&lt;div id=<span class=\"string\">&quot;test-editor&quot;</span>&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &lt;textarea style=&quot;display:none;&quot;&gt;### 关于 Editor.md</span><br><span class=\"line\">        **Editor.md** 是一款开源的、可嵌入的 Markdown 在线编辑器（组件），基于 CodeMirror、jQuery 和 Marked 构建。</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &lt;/textarea&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;/div&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>3.js</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight javascript\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$(<span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">function</span>(<span class=\"params\"></span>) </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">var</span> editor = editormd(<span class=\"string\">&quot;test-editor&quot;</span>, &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"comment\">// width  : &quot;100%&quot;,</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"comment\">// height : &quot;100%&quot;,</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        path   : <span class=\"string\">&quot;editormd/lib/&quot;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;);</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>结果应如官网所示：（个人项目暂时不方便贴图）<br><img src=\"https://pic.downk.cc/item/5e188a527f9a96fec163a538.jpg\"><br>向form表单中传值时只需传写好的textarea即可。</p>\n<h3 id=\"预览模式的配置\"><a href=\"#预览模式的配置\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"预览模式的配置\"></a>预览模式的配置</h3><p>1.导包(注意路径)</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight javascript\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&lt;!--JavaScript--&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;script src=<span class=\"string\">&quot;js/jquery.min.js&quot;</span>&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;script src=<span class=\"string\">&quot;../lib/marked.min.js&quot;</span>&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;script src=<span class=\"string\">&quot;../lib/prettify.min.js&quot;</span>&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;script src=<span class=\"string\">&quot;../lib/raphael.min.js&quot;</span>&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;script src=<span class=\"string\">&quot;../lib/underscore.min.js&quot;</span>&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;script src=<span class=\"string\">&quot;../lib/sequence-diagram.min.js&quot;</span>&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;script src=<span class=\"string\">&quot;../lib/flowchart.min.js&quot;</span>&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;script src=<span class=\"string\">&quot;../lib/jquery.flowchart.min.js&quot;</span>&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;script src=<span class=\"string\">&quot;../editormd.js&quot;</span>&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>2.html</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight javascript\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&lt;div id=<span class=\"string\">&quot;test-editormd-view2&quot;</span>&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &lt;textarea id=&quot;append-test&quot; style=&quot;display:none;&quot;&gt;### 关于 Editor.md</span><br><span class=\"line\">        **Editor.md** 是一款开源的、可嵌入的 Markdown 在线编辑器（组件），基于 CodeMirror、jQuery 和 Marked 构建。</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &lt;/textarea&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;/div&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>3.js</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight javascript\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$(<span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">function</span>(<span class=\"params\"></span>) </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">var</span> testEditormdView2;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    testEditormdView2 = editormd.markdownToHTML(<span class=\"string\">&quot;test-editormd-view2&quot;</span>, &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                htmlDecode      : <span class=\"string\">&quot;style,script,iframe&quot;</span>,  <span class=\"comment\">// you can filter tags decode</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">                emoji           : <span class=\"literal\">true</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">                taskList        : <span class=\"literal\">true</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">                tex             : <span class=\"literal\">true</span>,  <span class=\"comment\">// 默认不解析</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">                flowChart       : <span class=\"literal\">true</span>,  <span class=\"comment\">// 默认不解析</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">                sequenceDiagram : <span class=\"literal\">true</span>,  <span class=\"comment\">// 默认不解析</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">            &#125;);</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>结果应如官网所示：（个人项目暂时不方便贴图）<br><img src=\"https://pic.downk.cc/item/5e188baf7f9a96fec163d9aa.jpg\"></p>\n","more":"<p>伴随着一系列的问题，大佬们也开始探索更完美的解决方案，而MarkDown语法便是大家目前公认的解决方案之一。它的优点主要就是统一方便的语法，可以让人们专注于创作——难道让我就想加个标题还得前后加个H1标签？<br>之后我便在github上找到了一款国产开源，适配简单的markdown编辑器<a href=\"https://pandao.github.io/editor.md/\">editormd</a>。功能覆盖的很全面，在这里我只说一下编辑模式，阅读模式怎么架到自己的项目里。</p>\n<h3 id=\"下载项目source\"><a href=\"#下载项目source\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"下载项目source\"></a>下载项目source</h3><p><a href=\"https://github.com/pandao/editor.md/archive/master.zip\">点击这里下载</a><br>接着移植的时候只需要以下文件和文件夹即可。<br><img src=\"https://pic.downk.cc/item/5e1888947f9a96fec1634e6a.jpg\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"编辑模式的配置\"><a href=\"#编辑模式的配置\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"编辑模式的配置\"></a>编辑模式的配置</h3><p>1.导包(注意路径)</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight javascript\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&lt;!--CSS--&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;link rel=<span class=\"string\">&quot;stylesheet&quot;</span> href=<span class=\"string\">&quot;editormd/css/editormd.css&quot;</span> /&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;!--JavaScript--&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;script src=<span class=\"string\">&quot;https://cdn.bootcss.com/jquery/1.11.3/jquery.min.js&quot;</span>&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;script src=<span class=\"string\">&quot;editormd/editormd.min.js&quot;</span>&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>2.html</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight javascript\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&lt;div id=<span class=\"string\">&quot;test-editor&quot;</span>&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &lt;textarea style=&quot;display:none;&quot;&gt;### 关于 Editor.md</span><br><span class=\"line\">        **Editor.md** 是一款开源的、可嵌入的 Markdown 在线编辑器（组件），基于 CodeMirror、jQuery 和 Marked 构建。</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &lt;/textarea&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;/div&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>3.js</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight javascript\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$(<span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">function</span>(<span class=\"params\"></span>) </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">var</span> editor = editormd(<span class=\"string\">&quot;test-editor&quot;</span>, &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"comment\">// width  : &quot;100%&quot;,</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"comment\">// height : &quot;100%&quot;,</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        path   : <span class=\"string\">&quot;editormd/lib/&quot;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;);</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>结果应如官网所示：（个人项目暂时不方便贴图）<br><img src=\"https://pic.downk.cc/item/5e188a527f9a96fec163a538.jpg\"><br>向form表单中传值时只需传写好的textarea即可。</p>\n<h3 id=\"预览模式的配置\"><a href=\"#预览模式的配置\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"预览模式的配置\"></a>预览模式的配置</h3><p>1.导包(注意路径)</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight javascript\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&lt;!--JavaScript--&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;script src=<span class=\"string\">&quot;js/jquery.min.js&quot;</span>&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;script src=<span class=\"string\">&quot;../lib/marked.min.js&quot;</span>&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;script src=<span class=\"string\">&quot;../lib/prettify.min.js&quot;</span>&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;script src=<span class=\"string\">&quot;../lib/raphael.min.js&quot;</span>&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;script src=<span class=\"string\">&quot;../lib/underscore.min.js&quot;</span>&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;script src=<span class=\"string\">&quot;../lib/sequence-diagram.min.js&quot;</span>&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;script src=<span class=\"string\">&quot;../lib/flowchart.min.js&quot;</span>&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;script src=<span class=\"string\">&quot;../lib/jquery.flowchart.min.js&quot;</span>&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;script src=<span class=\"string\">&quot;../editormd.js&quot;</span>&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>2.html</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight javascript\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&lt;div id=<span class=\"string\">&quot;test-editormd-view2&quot;</span>&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &lt;textarea id=&quot;append-test&quot; style=&quot;display:none;&quot;&gt;### 关于 Editor.md</span><br><span class=\"line\">        **Editor.md** 是一款开源的、可嵌入的 Markdown 在线编辑器（组件），基于 CodeMirror、jQuery 和 Marked 构建。</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &lt;/textarea&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;/div&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>3.js</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight javascript\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$(<span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">function</span>(<span class=\"params\"></span>) </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">var</span> testEditormdView2;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    testEditormdView2 = editormd.markdownToHTML(<span class=\"string\">&quot;test-editormd-view2&quot;</span>, &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                htmlDecode      : <span class=\"string\">&quot;style,script,iframe&quot;</span>,  <span class=\"comment\">// you can filter tags decode</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">                emoji           : <span class=\"literal\">true</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">                taskList        : <span class=\"literal\">true</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">                tex             : <span class=\"literal\">true</span>,  <span class=\"comment\">// 默认不解析</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">                flowChart       : <span class=\"literal\">true</span>,  <span class=\"comment\">// 默认不解析</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">                sequenceDiagram : <span class=\"literal\">true</span>,  <span class=\"comment\">// 默认不解析</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">            &#125;);</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>结果应如官网所示：（个人项目暂时不方便贴图）<br><img src=\"https://pic.downk.cc/item/5e188baf7f9a96fec163d9aa.jpg\"></p>","categories":[{"name":"开发","path":"api/categories/开发.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"js插件","path":"api/tags/js插件.json"},{"name":"前端","path":"api/tags/前端.json"}]}